In the old days you could see what all the peeps on Twitter were raving about, and then, in an incredibly time-consuming process, pick up the remote and switch to that channel - or implement the DVR strategy of your choice. That, of course, ran a grave risk that you might while wrestling with the remote miss a choice jewel tumbling down the social networking waterfall.
